{"lastModified":1768901564226,"uri":"c::32018258056::vessel::64e27a00-4b56-11f0-91ef-fbcca8c705e8","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nCheck-in: Saturday from 17:00h  |  Check-out: Saturday until 09:00h\n\nThe brand new Hanse 508 shares many elements with the larger Hanse 548 Mila Felice we have in our fleet , from the same sail locker, owners cabin with ensuite back to the versatile heads, which can be a head and walk in shower, heads and fully equipped utility room.\n\nHanse 508 Evelyn is the perfect yacht for relaxed blue water sailing, with its progressive design and one of the most thrilling performance levels of its class. With a fascinating interior and an exceptionally diverse range of clever customisation options. The Hanse 508 lives up to the highest standards of flexibility, style and quality of life. Let yourself be amazed by excellent luxury.\n\nAvailable for Wednesday-Wednesday Charter in season 2023! Start a new trend with us and avoid crowded marinas on Saturday and enjoy more relaxed arriving in our base!\n\nOur Hanse 508 Evelyn offers from 8+1 berths and 3 heads, including air condition, generator, electric toilets and BBQ in cockpit! Bow thruster and stern thruster in addition makes it really easy to sail even with smaller crew!","blueprint":{"name":"EVELYN","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::64e27a00-4b56-11f0-91ef-fbcca8c705e8::assets::42072961-4b5e-11f0-8579-2119810bcfa7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::64e27a00-4b56-11f0-91ef-fbcca8c705e8::assets::42041c20-4b5e-11f0-8579-2119810bcfa7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::64e27a00-4b56-11f0-91ef-fbcca8c705e8::assets::42068d20-4b5e-11f0-8579-2119810bcfa7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::64e27a00-4b56-11f0-91ef-fbcca8c705e8::assets::4205a2c0-4b5e-11f0-8579-2119810bcfa7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::64e27a00-4b56-11f0-91ef-fbcca8c705e8::assets::42097350-4b5e-11f0-8579-2119810bcfa7/{imageVariant}","/